    "description": "<strong>与不同魔物对抗</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/1f111cfea7918c4463f9c58d301e5e46.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/1f111cfea7918c4463f9c58d301e5e46.webm?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/1f111cfea7918c4463f9c58d301e5e46.mp4?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在每局游戏中，你将面对众多怪物。 与它们战斗并尽可能存活下来。<br><br><strong>强化角色</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/4801dbbccd6cf528a6105e85d27fe6aa.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/4801dbbccd6cf528a6105e85d27fe6aa.webm?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/4801dbbccd6cf528a6105e85d27fe6aa.mp4?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>当你击败一定数量的怪物时，你的角色将会升级，并有机会选择一件魔法物品。<br><br><strong>制作物品</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/b700179e636f08f37796ffb327f08672.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/b700179e636f08f37796ffb327f08672.webm?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/b700179e636f08f37796ffb327f08672.mp4?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你也可以利用木材来制作物品。<br><br><strong>击败最终BOSS</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/80cc3c91c9d42e79a77e37aa0e175e34.poster.avif?t=1766178979\" width=800 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/80cc3c91c9d42e79a77e37aa0e175e34.webm?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2113770/extras/80cc3c91c9d42e79a77e37aa0e175e34.mp4?t=1766178979\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>生存一定的时间后，击败最终Boss以取得胜利。",
